description: It's a shame when young people are too lazy to pursue their dreams, such a waste of potential. This young man dreamed to be and architect but was too lazy to do something about it. Instead he ended up working at various warehouses as a forklift operator. The jobs weren't very good so I found him a warehouse with better paid staff. The poor dude was broke because his cheating ex-girlfriend was sucking money out of him for years before the break-up. He was so skint he couldn't afford to pay our mediation fee. Well, I had my plans with the guy so it wasn't a big problem. I was also going to improve his financial situation a lot. My mind was full of ideas... I just needed this guy to be reasonable and let me help him. I even brought a few toys to make his tight ass ready for me. I think it worked.
title: Dirty Scout 222
